ygData.messageBody:
I am a guide again on the Rodcet Nife server, my guide name is Zute.

Technically I am not supposed to inform you all I am a guide there. This
is to avoid preferential treatment and such. I'm not going to give anyone
preferential treatment, but please feel free to chat with me and say hi =)

If you do have a problem and I am online please petition normally and
allow whatever guide who gets the petition to handle it. If you encounter
homophobia on the other hand, please feel free to send me a direct tell.

Rainbow power!

- Zute
